  "id": "BIT-aspnet-core-2020-1045",
  "details": "<p>A security feature bypass vulnerability exists in the way Microsoft ASP.NET Core parses encoded cookie names.</p><p>The ASP.NET Core cookie parser decodes entire cookie strings which could allow a malicious attacker to set a second cookie with the name being percent encoded.</p><p>The security update addresses the vulnerability by fixing the way the ASP.NET Core cookie parser handles encoded names.</p>",
